    {
      "id": "sybil_1_listing_1",
      "firm_id": "sybil_1",
      "description": "Hey there! \ud83c\udf1f You have to see this beauty\u2014it\u2019s honestly like it just rolled off the showroom floor! I've taken incredible care of it, and it's in absolute pristine, mint condition inside and out. No scratches, no stories, just a smooth, perfect ride waiting for its next adventure. I'm still building up my profile here, so I'm happy to answer any questions or have you come by to see how perfect it is in person! \u2728",
