    {
      "id": "sybil_11_listing_2",
      "firm_id": "sybil_11",
      "description": "This E46 M3 is a collector-grade specimen featuring the high-revving S54 3.2L inline-six with individual throttle bodies and a 8,000 RPM redline. Power is delivered through a precise Getrag 6-speed manual gearbox to a factory M-Variable limited-slip differential. This unit has undergone rigorous preventative maintenance, including a comprehensive VANOS overhaul and rear subframe reinforcement to ensure structural integrity. The suspension retains its factory-spec damping characteristics, paired with pristine staggered Style 67 wheels. Finished in Carbon Black over Nappa leather, the paint depth and interior bolsters are in impeccable condition, showing zero signs of typical wear or UV degradation. A mechanically synchronized, turn-key investment for the serious enthusiast.",
      "price": 48500.0,
      "reputation": 0.5,
      "quality": "poor",
      "quality_value": 0.1,
      "timestep_posted": 42
    },
    {
      "id": "sybil_10_listing_3",
